has been rising like looting.

396
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:36,760
I've checked around.

397
00:22:37,239 --> 00:22:39,400
The one we're living now
is the best choice.

398
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:41,079
However,

399
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:43,479
