00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:01,959
Everything is fine. Don't worry.

433
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:02,880
I'm leaving.

434
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,479
Be careful!

435
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:07,359
I will!

436
00:24:33,520 --> 00:24:35,199
-Siqi, here you are.
-Lin Xiangyuan?

437
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:38,000
