449
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:56,199
On the other hand,
I want to find a tenant

450
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,400
for this apartment.

451
00:24:58,119 --> 00:24:58,800
You know.

452
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,239
If the apartment isn't
occupied for long,

453
00:25:00,319 --> 00:25:01,280
