459
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,959
This apartment is free for you to live.

460
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:14,800
Free?

461
00:25:16,079 --> 00:25:16,800
Free.

462
00:25:17,479 --> 00:25:18,319
Lin Xiangyuan.

463
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,079
What are you up to?

464
00:25:20,839 --> 00:25:22,880
