488
00:26:28,839 --> 00:26:30,119
But I'm really sorry.

489
00:26:30,560 --> 00:26:31,880
I don't know your friend.

490
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,160
I can't accept it.

491
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,959
In this case,

492
00:26:35,359 --> 00:26:36,280
