493
00:26:36,439 --> 00:26:37,680
No, no. Siqi,

494
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:39,319
don't get me wrong.

495
00:26:40,359 --> 00:26:42,079
I swear to God,

496
00:26:42,199 --> 00:26:44,079
