505
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:04,839
Fine, I know

506
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:07,839
in your mind, I am

507
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:10,119
a person to sail with the wind,

508
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,719
