542
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,640
Siqi,

543
00:29:03,719 --> 00:29:04,719
please.

544
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:06,599
Will you?

545
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:17,359
Thank you.

546
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:23,560
